&lt;p&gt;We are in search of an Associate Legal Counsel for Korea. This role reports to the Associate General Counsel - Northeast Asia. This role also supports the Legal Counsel within the Korea Legal Team and serves as legal partner to many other teams outside Legal. Collaboration will be a key attribute as this role will work very closely with the other members of the legal team both in the region and globally. This role needs to be based in &lt;strong&gt;Seoul, Korea.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as an effective and trusted partner to the fast-paced and high-performing Airbnb team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver clear, effective and practical legal advice to the various business functions. These include business development, public policy, marketing and communications.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
